# Design Insights - Day 1 (Jan 3, 2026)
**The Design of Everyday Things - Ch1: Psychopathology (21 pages)**

## Key Concepts Understood:
1. **Norman Doors** - Confusing designs needing "PUSH/PULL" signs = design failure
2. **Affordances** - Object signals what I CAN do (chair shape = sit)
3. **Signifiers** - Object shows HOW to do it (handle = pull, plate = push)

**Application**: My p5.js shapes = good discoverability (center placement = focal point)
**Tomorrow**: Mouse interaction = perfect signifier example

